data.description: Step into your ideal home! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home features easy-to-maintain tile floors throughout. The spacious living room, with its high ceilings, is perfect for relaxation or entertaining. Continue to the kitchen, complete with a peninsula perfect for additional seating and a breakfast nook with views to your backyard. The formal dining room provides another space to entertain or a flexible space to customize to your needs. Parking is a breeze with the attached 2-car garage, complete with a convenient screen for enjoying the outdoors without unwanted guests. Step into the enclosed porch providing additional living space with access to a spacious backyard. Don't miss the chance to make this home yours - schedule a showing today!
